            "id": 6007567,
            "title": "史上最危險陰謀！川普下令徹查拜登 「隱病由他人執政」",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普周四 (5 日) 下令徹查拜登任內一系列政策文件的簽署過程與合法性，以及其幕僚是否有隱瞞拜登的心理或身體健康狀況。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007567%2Fl%2F72689099c9a279802121a0a4d998a540.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">史上最危險陰謀！川普下令徹查拜登 「隱病由他人執政」。(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普簽署一份總統備忘錄，指示司法部長邦迪（Pam Bondi）與白宮法律顧問沃靈頓（David Warrington）進行調查，並提及拜登使用自動簽名機簽署文件的情況。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>自動簽名機是一種機械裝置，可複製某人真實的簽名，數十年來多位美國總統皆曾使用。然而，川普多次暗示拜登的一些政策無效，理由是其幕僚奪取了總統職權，以掩蓋川普所謂的拜登「認知衰退」。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>備忘錄也指出，調查範圍應涵蓋是否有個人或團體協調行動，刻意隱匿拜登的健康資訊，或在總統本人狀態不清時，由其他人行使職權。文件中提到，若屬實，相關行為「可能構成違憲」。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普在備忘錄中寫道：「這場陰謀是美國歷史上最危險、最令人憂慮的醜聞之一，美國公眾被刻意蒙蔽，無從得知究竟是誰在行使行政權力，而拜登的簽名卻被大量使用在數千份文件上，推動激進政策的轉變。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
